Class Student

java.lang.Object
io.mygame.entities.Entity
io.mygame.entities.NPC
io.mygame.entities.Student
Direct Known Subclasses:
Student.CollegeFemale1, Student.CollegeFemale2, Student.CollegeMale1, Student.CollegeMale2
public abstract class Student extends NPC
Abstract class representing a Student, which is a type of NPC in the game. A Student has unique characteristics and movement types, inheriting behavior from the NPC class.

  • Constructor Details

    • Student

      public Student(String fileName, float x, float y, String movementType, String npcType)
      Constructs a Student instance with the specified file name, position, movement type, and NPC type.
      Parameters:
      fileName - the file path of the sprite image for the Student.
      x - the initial x-coordinate of the Student.
      y - the initial y-coordinate of the Student.
      movementType - the movement type of the Student (e.g., targeted, horizontal, etc.).
      npcType - the type of Student (e.g., MaleStudent, FemaleStudent).
